  <brief_title>A 5 Day Course of Fludarabine and Cytarabine Followed by Full Intensity Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation (FA5-Bucy) in Treating Patients With High-risk, Recurrent or Refractory Acute Leukemia and Advanced Myelodysplastic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 5 Day Course of Fludarabine and Cytarabine Followed by Full Intensity Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation (FA5-Bucy) in Treating Patients With High-risk, Recurrent or Refractory Acute Leukemia and Advanced Myelodysplastic Syndrome</official_title>
