    <description>Fludarabine (F) 30 mg/m²/day for 5 days (day -12 to day-8) Cytarabine (A) 2g/m²/day for 5 days (day -12 to day-8) Bulsufan (Bu) 0.8mg/kg/day for 3 days (day -7 to day-5) Cyclophosphamide(Cy) 1.8g/m²/day for 3 days (day -4 to day-3)</description>
